{SPEED ATTACKER} (This creature doesn't get summoning sickness.)
{DOUBLE BREAKER}
■ Whenever this creature attacks, Armored Mechraid 8. Armored {MECHRAID} 8 - Look at the top 3 cards of your deck. From among them, you may use a Armored card that costs 8 or less for no cost. Put the rest on the bottom of your deck in any order.

​{TRIPLE BREAKER}
■ When you put this creature, put all Fire Birds in your graveyard into your hand.
■ Once per turn, whenever one of your Armored Dragons would be destroyed, you may put a Fire Bird from your hand instead.

{DOUBLE BREAKER}
■ When this creature would be discarded from your hand during your opponent's turn, put it instead.
■ When you put this creature, choose one of your opponent's creatures that has "blocker" and destroy it.

{DOUBLE BREAKER}
■ When you put this creature, reveal the top 3 cards of your deck. Put all Armored Dragons and Fire Birds from among them into your hand, and put the rest on the bottom of your deck in any order. If all the revealed cards were Dragons, this creature gets "speed attacker" until the end of the turn. (A creature that has "speed attacker" doesn't get "summoning sickness".)
■ When this creature would be discarded during your opponent's turn, you may put it instead.
